---
title: Quick Honey, Soy & Ginger Pork Meatballs with Ponzu Slaw & Peanuts
description: Fragrance, aromas and flavours, tick all those boxes with these pork meatballs. The honey-soy glaze adds a touch of sweet and salty goodness, perfect for ginger pork meatballs. That’s a wrap on our dinner to-do list!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
